txt.en: Throne of the Dread Terror: The Summoned -- Tier 1

The twisted rogmul, Vadokhar, has been called forth from the Void. This terrible creature is beyond the skill of many fighting on the field and must be banished before it can wreak havoc on the defenders of Gondor.
